HEADWORD: Subbreed
<hw>Sub"breed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A race or strain differing in certain characters from the parent
breed; an incipient breed.</def>⟦br⟧
